    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4573351>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4573355>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4573353>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4573357> ;
